# Architecture

- Put domain logic in `src/features/<domain>/` (stores, services, selectors, hooks).
- Keep `src/pages/` thin: wire a view or feature entry only.
- Shared domain types live in `src/types/desktop.ts` — do not duplicate launcher/settings shapes.
- UI primitives go in `src/components/` (`comic/` for design-system pieces, `shell/` for chrome).
- Prefer Zustand stores over React Context for domain state.
- User-facing strings and error messages stay in Spanish; code identifiers stay in English.
- Do not grow `pages/` into business logic hubs.
